Using a sliver of a victim's bone, the sorcerer transforms the shard into<br>
a bolt of energy that strikes at a target with unerring accuracy. <br>
Although a basic offensive spell, it can be a useful first strike at an<br>
unsuspecting foe, the impaling dart causing a fair amount of shock and<br>
damage.<br>
